ot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;element_pack_global_tooltip_border_radius_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true}}\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-568f936 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"568f936\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c39e41f\" data-id=\"c39e41f\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d3e15f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8d3e15f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If you were around in the events industry many years ago, you will probably be used to something like this if you wanted to conduct a poll.<\/p><p>While effective,\u00a0voting through one of these keypads not only seems unresponsive as it is a one way communication, it look outdated and clunky. \u00a0Managing a large number of\u00a0devices in a crowd without one of them going missing, getting damaged or not working is\u00a0also a big logistical issue.<\/p><p>While this technology is still available today, and works perfectly fine, why not go for something more refined, more convenient and a lot cooler!\u00a0With\u00a0mobile applications and engagement solutions,<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>engaging\u00a0your audience is simple, quick and in the palm of your attendees!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3fb661f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3fb661f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"336\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/Micepad-Live-Polling-Display.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3899\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/Micepad-Live-Polling-Display.jpeg 700w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/Micepad-Live-Polling-Display-300x144.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0bccebe elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0bccebe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Using their very own mobile phones, polls can be administered with the results shown live on the screen. This has not only become a handy way to get everyone involved, but also a good way to start a discussion with poll results giving the flow and direction. It is also versatile in it\u2019s uses.<\/p><p>Want to find out what the crowd thinks? Do a poll before your presentation and do another one right after and see the change in their understanding and knowledge.<\/p><p>Not sure of how to carry on the discussion? Plan polls during your panel discussion and use them if you need interesting insights to discuss.<\/p><p>Want to give out a prize? Get the audience to vote for the winner live on screen!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6196d9d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6196d9d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"336\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/Micepad-Live-Polling-Display.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3899\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/Micepad-Live-Polling-Display.jpeg 700w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/Micepad-Live-Polling-Display-300x144.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a6e37c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5a6e37c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>As you can see. a poll can come in handy at several points during your conference. But be sure to never create a poll for the sake of creating one. Doing this might lead to lower participation and resistance to participation as not only does it get repetitive after a while, it might even feel irritating. Don\u2019t turn a positive to a negative. Use it wisely!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32119a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"32119a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"367\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/micepad-live-polls-on-projector-screen.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3901\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/micepad-live-polls-on-projector-screen.jpg 768w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2017\/03\/micepad-live-polls-on-projector-screen-300x143.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e40e98 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8e40e98\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Now that you\u2019ve had these insights, how likely are you to use a poll for your next event?<\/p><p>A. Very Likely<br \/>B. Likely<br \/>C. Not Likely<br \/>D. Not At All<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you were around in the events industry many years ago, you will probably be used to something like this if you [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2705,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[131,133],"tags":[120],"class_list":["post-2671","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-how-to-tutorials","category-industry-insights","tag-event-management"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2671","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"em